      data-aos="fade-up"
      data-aos-duration="2000">
      </div>

      <p
        class="text-base lg:col-start-1 lg:row-start-2  leading-relaxed"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-duration="2000"
      >
        I'm a self-taught full stack engineer with Big Data Experience. I love 
        bringing ideas to life with code and owning products end to end. 
        
        I have worked across start ups and larger organizations. I love developing solutions that benefit society
        especially projects in the emerging Green Tech Space

      </p>
      <p
        class="text-base lg:row-start-3 leading-relaxed "
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-duration="2500"
      >
      This site is currently written using Astro, Typescript, Tailwind CSS and uses Python for backed Data Processes in the background.
      </p>
      <p
        class="text-base un lg:col-start-2 lg:row-start-2 "
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-duration="2500"
      >
        This site is currently written using Astro, Typescript, Tailwind CSS and uses Python for backed Data Processes in the background.
        This enables this site to be rendered and served as a static webpage without there being any need to provision a Database or Server management.
        All Data processes are run locally and then pushed to GitHub to be built. 

      </p>
      <p
        class="text-base lg:col-start-2 lg:row-start-3 "
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-duration="3000"
      >
      Deployed using GitHub actions mean that I can automatically deploy this site whenever the underlying data changes. Using a standard workflow,
      the only limiting factor for deploying this is the free amount of build minutes per month on GitHub.
      </p>
      <p
      class="text-base lg:col-start-3 lg:row-start-2 "
      data-aos="fade-up"
      data-aos-duration="3000"
    >
      I am passionate about building projects that can stand the test of time and use best practices improving productivity and 
      enabling innovation for the future.
    </p>
    <p
    class="text-base lg:col-start-3 lg:row-start-3 "
    data-aos="fade-up"
    data-aos-duration="3000"
  >
  I am currently available for Enquires. If you need a landing page, data pipeline
  or just want to ideate on new products, do not hesitate to get in
  contact.
  </p>
